            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_33gc' title='Col. 33GC &mdash; HL Deb 12 October 1999 vol 605 c33GC' name='column_33gc' href='#column_33gc' rel='bookmark'>33GC</a>
            big trees from little acorns grow, and if small producers are discouraged at an early stage they may not help British industry.
