            It I can take the report first, from my understanding of what the Minister has said to us that will come to us before Parliament rises in the summer.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0605P0-02053'>
        <a name='S5LV0605P0_19991012_GCR_171'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-helene-hayman' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
