        Clause 8 [<span class="italic">Acquisition and review of information</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0605P0-02129'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0605P0_19991012_GCR_247' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
